JobName: 00. Prepare Log Tables and Test Execution

Tasks.JobName: 00. Prepare Log Tables and Test Execution
Tasks.TaskContent:
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.ExecutionLog'))
BEGIN
	EXEC (N'CREATE TABLE dbo.ExecutionLog (ExecutionDatetime datetime, TargetConnection varchar(50), TestCaseID nvarchar(10), TestResult nvarchar(10), ErrorDescription nvarchar(1000))');
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	TRUNCATE TABLE dbo.ExecutionLog;
END

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.ExecutionLogArchive'))
BEGIN
	EXEC (N'CREATE TABLE dbo.ExecutionLogArchive (ArchiveDatetime datetime, ExecutionDatetime datetime, TargetConnection varchar(50), TestCaseID nvarchar(10), TestResult nvarchar(10), ErrorDescription nvarchar(1000))');
END
